data.value:
Description: This system will keep files safe. It will also reduce the amount of work to be done and will speed up processes for billing and reservation transactions.
The system can store the records of different clients.
The system has a database which where the information will be kept. It can be also used as a reference.
The system can handle reservation services better.
The staff can easily detect available rooms for new clients.
The system can reduce data redundancy.
